text: We got a table at 6.30pm om Friday without any problem. Place is not very busy. Steady steam of customer but not packed. The menu has a large selection of pasta, rice bowl and western. All are good. There is no dessert. The cafe only open for dinner Fri to Sun. Parking outside is free.

Came a few times and it's consistently good! Highly recommend this place for their great food and ambience - the vibes are laid back and perfect for chilling the weekend away (or pretend it's the weekend).

Milkshakes are to die for!

I was craving for pasta and came here to get one for lunch. It was great. I loved the pasta with crispy pork and the egg on top.

Can customize own pasta but didn't try it yet. Maybe next time.

I would come back again to try their other pasta whenever I am craving for one.

This restaurant has been a reliable spot for delicious pasta over the years. The dishes are made to order with fresh ingredients, ensuring great flavour and quality.

The dining environment is clean and comfortable, with light music that adds to the relaxed atmosphere. A great place for a satisfying meal.

Nice quiet cafe… came here in the afternoon for some work. Ordered a Spam Fries ($9.5) and the amount i was given was… miserable :(

other than that.. all good.
